\noindent \textbf{Mr. G. D. Consultant} has significant experience in economic analysis, consulting, reporting, research, and studies in various parts of the world. He has worked in senior positions for many development projects for a number of multi-lateral and bi-lateral donor organizations. His education includes a degree in history, a Master?s Degree in Business Administration and a Master of Arts Degree in International Relations. His broad professional experience ranges from consulting to teaching.  In graduate school, he completed training in alternative dispute resolution and an intensive course in the Japanese language. He currently resides in Tokyo. \\
